title: Could potentially be used in place of general anaesthesia
More easily keep in touch with people overseas
Easier to travel both for leisure and business
Government and police may also use it to control people
comment: Police already abuse their power with pepper spray, guns, and any other means they can. If they had access to an app that could cause whole crowds of people to fall asleep at the touch of a button, they would abuse that power too.

title: Good for elderly people, pets etc. where anaethesia may be dangerous
Help people with insomnia and sleep disorders
Less physical harm than existing methods of control
More difficult to get a job etc without one
